4 A BILL
5 TO BE ENTITLED
6 AN ACT
7
8
9 Relating to Jefferson County; to authorize the city
10 council to establish additional entertainment districts in
11 Vestavia Hills.
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
13 Section 1. Notwithstanding any other provision of law,
14 the City Council of Vestavia Hills, by ordinance, may
15 establish up to five total entertainment districts within the
16 city permitting consumption of alcoholic beverages purchased
17 from on-premises alcoholic beverage licenses to be consumed by
18 purchasers anywhere within the entertainment districts. The
19 term on-premises as applied to consumption of alcoholic
20 beverages in each entertainment district shall include
21 anywhere within the district.
22 Section 2. This act shall become effective immediately.
